701681f-a.text:
Quincey Ave. (street running from right to left on which 2-story house are facing), east side, south from Philip (right) to but not including Randall Ave. The view shows the rears of the houses facing on the aforementioned avenue as seen across Calhoun Ave. (foreground) from its S.E. corner of Philip Ave.

July 9, 1928.

P.L. Sperr.
